SIMPLE: whereby
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whereby
<hw>Where*by"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>By which; -- used relatively.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧You take
my life when you take the means <xex>whereby</xex> I life.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>By what; how; -- used interrogatively.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Whereby</qex> shall I know this?</q> <rj><qau>Luke i.
18.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Where'er</ent>⟦br⟧
